Package gp

Class Summary
Crossover This class represents crossover functionality.
EquationGraphPanel This class represents a JPanel with a XY chart that compares the target equation with the evolved equation.
FindThread This class represents a thread that finds the equation using genetic programming
Fitness A class to compare produced outputs with expected results.
FunctionalSet A class that represents the functional set.
GeneticProgramming Primary class and GUI that starts the application
Mutation A class file that can change the value of a random node.
Node A class the represents a binary tree node.
PopulationFitnessPanel A chart panel that displays the fitness distribution in a pie chart.
TerminalSet A class that represents the terminal set.
Tree A class file that represents a binary tree A complete binary tree is a binary tree in which every level, except possibly the last, is completely filled, and all nodes are as far left as possible.
